Benefits: No standard benefits
Test Case 3: Input Validation - Invalid Email

text
Select Employee Type:
1. Full-Time Employee
2. Contractor
1
Enter Employee ID: FTE103
Enter Name: Charlie Brown
Enter Email: charlie.brown
Invalid email address. Must contain '@'.
Test Case 4: Input Validation - Negative Salary

text
